name: HyperbolicTrigonometryCalculator
0:
”Alexa, ask Hyperbolic Trigonometry Calculator what the hyperbolic sine of twenty is.”
”Alexa, tell Hyperbolic Trigonometry Calculator to calculate the hyperbolic tangent of fifty.”
”Alexa, ask Hyperbolic Trigonometry Calculator what the inverse hyperbolic cosine of three is.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hyperbolic trigonometry calculator
des:
Calculates the hyperbolic sine, cosine, and tangent of integers. Also calculates the inverse hyperbolic sine, cosine, and tangent of integers.
Integers that are very huge (positive or negative values) are not supported. Decimals, complex numbers, and fractions are not supported inputs.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
